    <p><h1>Raiding</h1></p>
    </p>
    <p>To focus more on PvP and Online Raiding, players are limited to 1x offline raid every 24 hrs. 
        When you start an offline raid your UI will trigger to 1/1 on the bottom right of your screen. 
        You will be locked out of any other offline raiding for 24hrs.</p>
    <p>This setting also helps to prevent people from being online 24/7 raiding the entire server while players are at work.</p>
    <p>The previous rule of no griefing has been lifted. 
    If you raid a base, you can now take the base over. Use it, seal it and let it decay it's up to you and just treated as game play.</p>
